Baseball_Bats.description: The Marucci Maple Wood Baseball Bats will have an approximate -3 length-to-weight ratio, perfect for any high school or college-aged player.
Genuine ash construction with a natural finish, the Louisville Slugger® Series 3X Ash Bat provides a large sweet spot and ideal bat speed that gets through the zone quickly.
Crafted for maximum strength and durability, the Mizuno® MZB-271 Classic Bamboo Bat provides players with a traditional look at the plate that’s built to last
